name: lonely days
description:
the table on the left is filled with lysol wipes, lysol spray, fresh hands and kleenex. it was march 2020. i had just gotten back from a trip in L.A., and now i had to quarantine for 14 days - alone, in my room, as to not get my parents sick in case i had caught covid-19 on the trip or on my way home. 

the only company i had was the warmth of the sun, beautiful sunsets and the sight of the moon. not to mention the tv, my nintendo switch and a speaker to listen to music, to distract myself from the horror that had just started globally, and the fear and uncertainty that it brought collectively as a consequence.
